issue.body:
With long `String` values with `YAMLGenerator.Feature.MINIMIZE_QUOTES` enabled, I have noticed the usage of quotes with some backslash `\` on new lines.

Example with `com.fasterxml.jackson.dataformat:jackson-dataformat-yaml:2.10.5`:

```yaml
---
a: This is a test
b: |-
  Fooo
  Fizz
  Baarr
  Test
c: "43"
d: very long long long Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec
  dignissim, velit in egestas consectetur, metus dui dignissim ipsum, et lacinia tellus
  purus vitae tortor. Vestibulum rhoncus ullamcorper eros, sit amet efficitur nulla
  hendrerit a. In posuere dignissim est at sollicitudin. Praesent suscipit placerat
  ligula, vitae pellentesque leo vestibulum eu. Aliquam in ante ac metus ultrices
  suscipit quis vitae erat. Maecenas feugiat sodales lectus quis elementum. Curabitur
  quis convallis mauris, eu vulputate nisi.
```

After the update `com.fasterxml.jackson.dataformat:jackson-dataformat-yaml:2.11.0` (and newer):

```yaml
---
a: This is a test
b: |-
  Fooo
  Fizz
  Baarr
  Test
c: "43"
d: "very long long long Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec\
  \ dignissim, velit in egestas consectetur, metus dui dignissim ipsum, et lacinia\
  \ tellus purus vitae tortor. Vestibulum rhoncus ullamcorper eros, sit amet efficitur\
  \ nulla hendrerit a. In posuere dignissim est at sollicitudin. Praesent suscipit\
  \ placerat ligula, vitae pellentesque leo vestibulum eu. Aliquam in ante ac metus\
  \ ultrices suscipit quis vitae erat. Maecenas feugiat sodales lectus quis elementum.\
  \ Curabitur quis convallis mauris, eu vulputate nisi."
```

Is this expected?

----

Reproducer using [jbang](https://www.jbang.dev/):

```java
///usr/bin/env jbang "$0" "$@" ; exit $?
	
//DEPS com.fasterxml.jackson.dataformat:jackson-dataformat-yaml:2.11.0
//DEPS org.yaml:snakeyaml:1.33

import static java.lang.System.*;
import com.fasterxml.jackson.dataformat.yaml.YAMLFactory;
import com.fasterxml.jackson.dataformat.yaml.YAMLGenerator;
import com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.ObjectMapper;
import com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.node.ObjectNode;

public class YamlExample {

    public static void main(String... args) throws Exception {
        YAMLFactory factory = YAMLFactory.builder()
            .enable(YAMLGenerator.Feature.MINIMIZE_QUOTES)
            .enable(YAMLGenerator.Feature.ALWAYS_QUOTE_NUMBERS_AS_STRINGS)
            .build();
        
        ObjectMapper mapper = new ObjectMapper(factory);

        ObjectNode tree = mapper.createObjectNode();
        tree.put("a", "This is a test");
        tree.put("b", "Fooo\nFizz\nBaarr\nTest");
        tree.put("c", "43");
        tree.put("d", "very long long long Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec dignissim, velit in egestas consectetur, metus dui dignissim ipsum, et lacinia tellus purus vitae tortor. Vestibulum rhoncus ullamcorper eros, sit amet efficitur nulla hendrerit a. In posuere dignissim est at sollicitudin. Praesent suscipit placerat ligula, vitae pellentesque leo vestibulum eu. Aliquam in ante ac metus ultrices suscipit quis vitae erat. Maecenas feugiat sodales lectus quis elementum. Curabitur quis convallis mauris, eu vulputate nisi.");

        out.println("Test yaml document:");

        String value = mapper.writer()
            .writeValueAsString(tree);
        out.println(value);
    }
}
```
